        Applies a vector to a set of locations
        Parameters:

        keepLiveFilter - Should we keep the vector angle persistent, or reset the particle vector each particle. Essentially (seg[n] = vec.multiply(vec.filter() * n)) if it is true; or (seg[n] = vec.multiply(vec.filter())) if it is false
